R會俾啲comment你個interview 做成點。<br />\n<br />\nPass左phone interview 之後你會即時收到email，約你去某個地方做group interview。我果日有20個人左右。第二round 主要都係香港既HR 見你，問返啲同phone interview 差唔多既問題，都輕鬆既，要記住講多啲故仔，share 下自己既經歷同埋呢啲經歷令你有咩反思。都係pass 左就會有電話通知你入唔入到下一round ，pass 唔到就會收到email。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:16:31.000Z","msg":"用普通話定英文？"},{"pid":"e438272386789867df87ca33ce0e2777ad2ac36e","tid":1265124,"uid":4686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:34:00.000Z","msg":"有冇人做緊 siri linguist既position <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e73c5a217d93dd56faea7bd16fbde2121016b4","tid":1265124,"uid":844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c65cf86dac40c65670852fd5848e4a7b848c18e","tid":1265124,"uid":77973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:17:21.000Z","msg":"IN 哂4輪, PHONE IN 一次,3次GROUP.<br />\n等左一個月OFFER 最後同我講唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:34:03.000Z","msg":"過左phone in 叫我下星期group in<br />\n點解你3次group咁多？主要問咩？有無講點解唔請"},{"pid":"9afe94d2c26788d7be8fcde5c9ef5a107a808e44","tid":1265124,"uid":844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ee0d06f69036b85c24ac761057bf3df84cf8c74","tid":1265124,"uid":20000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bfc68590c5b70fdb0c9f8b23b40a0165c1a06747","tid":1265124,"uid":20000,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bd77ad9856886da565df28e3bf3b7aa9f7566556","tid":1265124,"uid":244641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:08:04.000Z","msg":"巴打詳細d得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:14:00.000Z","msg":"第一round 係phone interview，同個上海既HR傾左一個鐘左右，主要都係先瞭解下點解你想做Apple，對Apple有啲咩感覺，同埋你自